latestIgtvVideos.title: Spoiler call to 2020
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
As we complete 1 year into the lockdown, we wish we knew a few things better about what we were getting into. We wish we could get some SPOILERS so we could avoid spoiling some of our best time. 

Since COVID-19 is like, "picture abhi baaki hai mere, dost" and preparing us for Lockdown Season 2, we thought we could let you have the best time from the comfort of your phones with us: @yuvaacampus - a safe space (including the pandemic) for ALL COLLEGE STUDENTS TO LIVE THE BEST OF THEIR COLLEGE LIFE. JOIN US NOW! 🥳🥳🥳

Video Credits: 
Cast: @spread_the_muskan
Written and directed by @iam_suyash
Creative Supervisor: @ishaubansall
Edited by: @theindefinikster
